headline: PayPal Needs Help From Its Oldest Friends—Consumers
summary: PayPal  is striking a lot of new partnerships in the payments and commerce business these days.  Venmo has been a huge brand and customer-acquisition asset for PayPal, as the product’s name became a verb and a ubiquitous peer-to-peer payment method.
